Text: I see you are adding to TPB geat albums from 'Pitchfork Best New Music' section. Thank you very much for that! It's really good music there. I'm really happy there are people like you. You've already uploaded a lot of albums from the section but I hope you will keep on this superb work (adding e.g. Department of Eagles or Jens Lekman or anything else from the section ). Thank you!
I asked for this. Thanks again!
Department of Eagles would be great :D
